title: Stompology: The Science of Ground-Shaking Steps

body.raw: "Salutations, earth-shakers and seismic scholars! Ever wondered how I manage to create earthquakes with every step? In this blog post, I'll peel back the layers of my stomping techniques and reveal the seismic secrets that make my presence felt."
